---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { TOOLS } from '../constants';

const title = '关于我们 - Momo工具箱';
const description = 'Momo工具箱是一个专注隐私的在线工具集合，提供 JSON、Markdown、二维码、密码生成等数十种实用工具，所有数据浏览器本地处理。';
const canonical = 'https://www.web-tools.top/about';
const toolCount = TOOLS.length;
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <article class="legal-page">
    {/* 静态 SEO 主标题：双语切换，保证页面有且仅有一个 h1 */}
    <h1 data-zh="关于 Momo工具箱" data-en="About Momo Toolbox">关于 Momo工具箱</h1>
    <p class="updated"><span data-zh="让工具更温暖一些" data-en="Tools, but warmer">让工具更温暖一些</span></p>

    <div data-lang="zh">
      <p>Momo工具箱是一个<strong>专注隐私</strong>的在线工具集合。我们提供 {toolCount}+ 种实用工具，覆盖文本处理、开发辅助、图像处理、效率提升等多个场景，所有数据均在浏览器本地处理，不上传服务器，即开即用。</p>

      <h2>我们的理念</h2>
      <p>市面上的在线工具网站大多存在两个问题：一是<strong>追踪用户</strong>，收集数据用于广告投放；二是<strong>体验糟糕</strong>，弹窗广告、慢速加载、操作繁琐。我们希望改变这个现状。</p>
      <p>Momo工具箱的核心理念：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>隐私优先</strong>：所有工具的数据处理都在你的浏览器完成，我们不收集任何个人身份信息</li>
        <li><strong>极速体验</strong>：基于 Astro 静态站点架构，页面预渲染 + 按需 hydrate，加载速度快如闪电</li>
        <li><strong>温暖设计</strong>：琥珀橙主色 + 柔和米色背景，告别冷冰冰的工具界面，让使用过程更愉悦</li>
        <li><strong>基础工具永久免费</strong>：基础工具功能无限制使用，无需注册、无付费墙</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>技术栈</h2>
      <p>我们使用现代前沿的 Web 技术栈构建：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>框架</strong>：Astro 5.18（Islands 架构，静态优先）</li>
        <li><strong>交互</strong>：React 19（仅在需要交互的组件上 hydrate）</li>
        <li><strong>样式</strong>：Tailwind CSS v4（原子化 CSS，零运行时开销）</li>
        <li><strong>部署</strong>：Cloudflare Pages（全球 CDN 加速）</li>
        <li><strong>双语</strong>：原生中英双语支持，跨组件同步切换</li>
      </ul>
      <p>这种架构带来的是<strong>极致的性能</strong>：首屏 HTML 仅几十 KB，所有静态资源通过全球 CDN 分发，无论你在世界哪个角落，都能获得毫秒级响应。</p>

      <h2>提供的工具</h2>
      <p>当前已上线 {toolCount} 个工具，覆盖以下类别：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>文本工具</strong>：Markdown 编辑器等</li>
        <li><strong>开发者工具</strong>：JSON 格式化、Base64、URL 编解码、时间戳、哈希、JWT 解码、UUID 等</li>
        <li><strong>图像工具</strong>：图片压缩等</li>
        <li><strong>效率工具</strong>：二维码生成、密码生成器、颜色转换、单位换算等</li>
      </ul>
      <p>我们持续添加新工具，欢迎通过邮箱告诉我们你的需求。</p>

      <h2>隐私承诺</h2>
      <p>我们高度重视你的隐私。具体来说：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>所有工具的输入输出都在你的浏览器处理，<strong>从不发送到服务器</strong></li>
        <li>我们不使用 Cookie 跟踪你</li>
        <li>我们使用 <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong>（隐私友好，无 Cookie，不跨站追踪）了解聚合的访问情况，不使用 Google Analytics 等追踪型分析服务</li>
        <li>仅使用 localStorage 保存语言、主题、收藏等 UI 偏好，数据仅存于你的设备</li>
        <li>第三方服务仅限 Cloudflare（托管与分析）和 Google Fonts（字体），它们有独立的隐私政策</li>
      </ul>
      <p>详情请查阅我们的<a href="/privacy">隐私政策</a>。</p>

      <h2>未来规划</h2>
      <p>我们正在持续扩展工具集，并探索以下方向：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>更多工具</strong>：HTTP 状态码查询、AES 加解密、番茄钟等即将上线</li>
        <li><strong>批量处理</strong>：批量图片压缩、批量 JSON 格式化等</li>
        <li><strong>用户系统</strong>：可选的账户系统，用于跨设备同步收藏和偏好</li>
        <li><strong>API 服务</strong>：为开发者提供工具 API 调用</li>
      </ul>
      <p>所有新增的<strong>基础工具</strong>都将<strong>永久免费</strong>。部分高级功能（如批量处理、API 高频调用）未来可能引入付费，但绝不会影响基础工具的免费使用。</p>

      <h2>联系我们</h2>
      <p>如果你有任何疑问、建议或发现了 bug，请通过邮箱联系我们：<a href="mailto:1902243211@qq.com">1902243211@qq.com</a>。</p>
      <p>我们会认真对待每一条反馈，并尽快回复你。</p>
    </div>

    <div data-lang="en">
      <p>Momo Toolbox is a <strong>privacy-focused</strong> collection of online tools. We offer {toolCount}+ practical tools covering text processing, developer utilities, image handling, productivity, and more. All data is processed locally in your browser — nothing is uploaded, instant and private.</p>

      <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
      <p>Most online tool websites suffer from two issues: <strong>user tracking</strong> for ad targeting, and <strong>poor UX</strong> with popups, slow loads, and clunky flows. We want to change that.</p>
      <p>Core principles of Momo Toolbox:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Privacy first</strong>: all tool processing happens in your browser. We collect no personally identifiable information</li>
        <li><strong>Blazing fast</strong>: built on Astro's static-first architecture with on-demand hydration — lightning quick</li>
        <li><strong>Warm design</strong>: amber accent + soft cream background, a humane alternative to cold tool UIs</li>
        <li><strong>Core tools free forever</strong>: unlimited use of core tool functionality, no registration, no paywall</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <p>Built with modern web technologies:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Framework</strong>: Astro 5.18 (Islands architecture, static-first)</li>
        <li><strong>Interactivity</strong>: React 19 (hydrated only where needed)</li>
        <li><strong>Styling</strong>: Tailwind CSS v4 (atomic CSS, zero runtime cost)</li>
        <li><strong>Hosting</strong>: Cloudflare Pages (global CDN)</li>
        <li><strong>Bilingual</strong>: native Chinese and English, synced across components</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This architecture delivers <strong>extreme performance</strong>: the initial HTML is just tens of KB, all static assets are served via global CDN, and you get millisecond-level response anywhere in the world.</p>

      <h2>Available Tools</h2>
      <p>{toolCount} tools are currently available across these categories:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Text tools</strong>: Markdown editor and more</li>
        <li><strong>Developer tools</strong>: JSON formatter, Base64, URL encoder, timestamp, hash, JWT decoder, UUID and more</li>
        <li><strong>Image tools</strong>: image compressor and more</li>
        <li><strong>Productivity</strong>: QR code generator, password generator, color converter, unit converter and more</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We are constantly adding new tools — feel free to email us your needs.</p>

      <h2>Privacy Commitment</h2>
      <p>We take your privacy seriously:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>All tool inputs and outputs are processed in your browser and <strong>never sent to a server</strong></li>
        <li>We do not use cookies to track you</li>
        <li>We use <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> (privacy-friendly, no cookies, no cross-site tracking) for aggregated traffic insights. We do not use tracking-based analytics like Google Analytics</li>
        <li>We only use localStorage for UI preferences (language, theme, favorites) — data stays on your device</li>
        <li>Third-party services are limited to Cloudflare (hosting and analytics) and Google Fonts (fonts), each with their own privacy policies</li>
      </ul>
      <p>See our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

      <h2>Future Plans</h2>
      <p>We are continuously expanding the toolset and exploring the following:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>More tools</strong>: HTTP status code lookup, AES encryption, Pomodoro timer coming soon</li>
        <li><strong>Batch processing</strong>: batch image compression, batch JSON formatting, etc.</li>
        <li><strong>User system</strong>: optional accounts to sync favorites and preferences across devices</li>
        <li><strong>API service</strong>: tool API access for developers</li>
      </ul>
      <p>All newly added <strong>core tools</strong> will <strong>remain free forever</strong>. Some advanced features (such as batch processing, high-frequency API calls) may introduce pricing in the future, but will never affect the free use of core tools.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions, suggestions, or bug reports, please email us at <a href="mailto:1902243211@qq.com">1902243211@qq.com</a>.</p>
      <p>We take every feedback seriously and reply as soon as possible.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <a href="/" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline;" data-zh="← 返回首页" data-en="← Back to Home">← 返回首页</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>